keyMappings:
# exit insert mode
mapkey I <c-[> 

map p passNextKey count=1
map <down> scrollDown
map <up> scrollUp
map <left> previousTab
map <right> nextTab

map n scrollDown
map e scrollUp
map h goBack
map l goForward
map <s-left> moveTabLeft
map <s-right> moveTabRight
map 0 firstTab
map $ lastTab
